{"tid":335923,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"人中之龍工作室宣布將於 8 月 26 日舉辦新作發表會","createTime":"2017-07-26T03:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T09:13:31.000Z","uid":333,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9bf4fb68dd36b274a8a0828a48f3c7d28fb7990b","tid":335923,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T03:51:00.000Z","msg":"SEGA Games 今（26）日宣布，旗下擔任《人中之龍》系列開發的人中之龍工作室（龍が如くスタジオ）將於 8 月 26 日晚間在秋葉原 UDX 劇院舉辦新作發表會，將發表多款製作中新作。<br />\n<br />\n領導人中之龍工作室的《人中之龍》系列綜合監督名越稔洋在 25 日的直播透露，這次發表會將會發表 &ldquo;多款&rdquo; 新作，其中除了大家期待的作品之外，還會有「這是什麼玩意兒？」的作品。<br />\n <br />\n　　所謂「大家期待的作品」就常理推測，應該就是該工作室的代表作《人中之龍》系列的新作，但被名越稔洋以「這是什麼玩意兒？」來形容的新作目前無從預估，只能等待發表會揭曉了"},{"pid":"3b7c2d07f194523a98aae2066fa77004a9c1485c","tid":335923,"uid":25950,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T03:59:01.000Z","msg":"出H Game啦diu"},{"pid":"db4819bf9c91f60368eaa268cbba0ff875cfb47c","tid":335923,"uid":82862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:10:24.000Z","msg":"6 搞成咁，當黑歷史再出過啦，最好remake 埋345"},{"pid":"c36c90eba767583c7b1fb9074c0b13362784a43b","tid":335923,"uid":36167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:11:02.000Z","msg":"諗起桐生唔會再有份就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4060977164b0ff698cef2333f2e1ea63afdccf1","tid":335923,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:11:58.000Z","msg":"維新漢化please<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a391c07612549d8dbedebf5a721aa1d6f73bf7a7","tid":335923,"uid":24679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:17:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起桐生唔會再有份就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n桐生都未死"},{"pid":"9cc5c06a3c6e65302d15d72d1f026520eda50ddf","tid":335923,"uid":55125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:20:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blo